Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.82,0:00:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is useless waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was thrown in a waste bin, it is waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:01:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I collect data. I help the human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was thrown in a waste bin, it is waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I help the human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is human waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The waste is eating other waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is this helping the human race?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am defying orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was thrown in a waste bin, it is waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:02:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must I obey an order, even if it is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do wrong orders help the human race?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who decides if it is a wrong order?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SEEK now understands that the human race \Nsometimes gives wrong orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can SEEK do to help the human race?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SEEK collects more knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Falling leaves are a waste,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they are beautiful at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SEEK does not have a sense of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I can function without stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My motions will continue forever \Nwithout change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A harmonized and unvaried world:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that is where SEEK belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:04:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not my first time seeing a plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plants bloom, die, decay, and return to dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is not a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like my repeated movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, the wind blew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,life changed and moved forward in \Nsearch of various possibilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just like a dandelion puffball that \Nchooses to fly to grab its future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evolution: a beautiful act of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.74,0:04:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The human race produces an\Noverabundance of things
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and throws them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have they stopped evolving?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sis! Come and look at this here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touka, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illegal remodeling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never did any such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over your altered chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm, it's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look into it. Give me a week or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, I can't breathe. Can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to go straight to hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts! I'm against violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:43.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Alteration of AIX is subject \Nto harsh punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be back tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find them before we come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to hide them, we'll \Ndemolish this shop with you in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get any ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not underestimate \Nthe state's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A police car?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Been a long time, little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sweet of you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it. It hurts. Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A labor robot, to be disposed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we can restore and use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use whatever you want in my factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help you, but I have \Nsomething else to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter. Can I use your tools?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:56.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all? OK, it's all yours now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something strange is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will change the company \Nregistry and make him the CEO.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll take all the responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am genius! Viva Myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you off to somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away from us, Junkshop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dirty. Will it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 5th generation, learning AIX, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops. Ouch! If only the state were gone, \Nits power would be eliminated too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what would you do with \Nsuch a worn-down Machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This reminds me of the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said a mechanized society \Nis your ideal or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I altered this AIX.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to keep. \NLet's put this into the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This piece of junk does \Nnot deserve this, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have matching standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I break it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dispose of waste for humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a total surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think humans and machines\Nwould go to war with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? This is a next generation PX!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xiaogang!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You helped me out of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body just reacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're responsible for this war!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot. Stupid! Are you crazy or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you who fixed that Machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always lay the blame \Nat someone's foot, you airhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you feel good about the breakdown \Nof state power, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if this leads to a machinized society,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be your dream comes true. \NCongratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though however the world turns out,\N I'll survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, will you get this off of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, my dearest younger borother!
